---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Services — Odin’s Vault" description="Landing pages, institutional sites, and MVP web apps — custom, fast, and conversion-ready.">
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:54px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Services</div>
      <h1 style="margin:14px 0 10px; font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.6vw, 3rem); letter-spacing:-0.04em;">
        What we build
      </h1>
      <p class="sub" style="max-width:820px;">
        We don’t limit you to a “cyber theme”. The <b>vault vibe</b> is a brand option — not a cage.
        The product is always custom.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Landing Page</h3>
          <p>1 page built to convert: offer, proof, pricing, CTA. Perfect for launches and campaigns.</p>
          <ul class="list" style="margin-top:12px;">
            <li>High-contrast modern design</li>
            <li>Mobile-first + performance</li>
            <li>Calendly + WhatsApp CTA</li>
            <li>GA-ready</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Institutional Website</h3>
          <p>Multi-page site that feels premium and trustworthy.</p>
          <ul class="list" style="margin-top:12px;">
            <li>About, Services, Tech, Proof, Contact</li>
            <li>SEO basics + analytics</li>
            <li>Fast static hosting (GitHub Pages)</li>
            <li>Easy to expand</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>MVP Web App + Landing</h3>
          <p>Validate your product idea with a real app, not a slide deck.</p>
          <ul class="list" style="margin-top:12px;">
            <li>Auth + core workflows</li>
            <li>Integrations as needed</li>
            <li>Admin + dashboards (when relevant)</li>
            <li>Landing page to sell it</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px;">
        <h3>Custom products (the “treasure” work)</h3>
        <p>
          If you want something unusual — interactive experiences, niche tooling, automation, integrations —
          that’s where we shine. Most agencies will say “too complicated”. We’ll ask: <b>what’s the simplest version that wins?</b>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="btnrow" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/your-next-devops/quick-chat" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Book a quick chat</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://wa.me/5548998142779" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href={`${Astro.base}/`}>Back home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
